      • CacheableBuilder

        public CacheableBuilder(CmsRequest<?> request)
        Constructor for Generators. Uses a default maximum expire time of 12 hours. If this isn't intended to be used directly by a Generator, use another constructor.
        Parameters:
        request - the request. A timestamp is added for the Request PageElement's last modified time.

      • setMaximumExpireTime

        public CacheableBuilder setMaximumExpireTime(TimeUnit unit,
                                    long value)
        Set the maximum expire time that is auto generated. If you call setExpireTime(long), the maximum expire time is ignored. Defaults to 12 hours.
        Parameters:
        unit - the unit.
        value - the value.
        Returns:
        this builder.
